    <item>
      <title>加密货币行业寄希望于重组后的 SEC 能在特朗普领导下复兴交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/trump-white-house-return-will-unleash-more-crypto-m-a-experts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 重返白宫后，加密货币行业支持的候选人在选举中以压倒性优势赢得了国会席位，数字资产合并热潮似乎已成定局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/trump-white-house-return-will-unleash-more-crypto-m-a-experts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币“混合器”因洗钱被判 12 年半监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/crypto-mixer-gets-150-months-for-bitcoin-fog-money-laundering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币混合服务公司 Bitcoin Fog 的创始人因从贩卖非法毒品的暗网市场洗钱数千万美元，被判处 12 年半监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/crypto-mixer-gets-150-months-for-bitcoin-fog-money-laundering</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 22:42:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德基金助力美国比特币 ETF 创下每日流入量纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/us-bitcoin-btc-etfs-including-blackrock-s-ibit-get-record-inflows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对数字资产行业的支持以及支持性监管的承诺推动，投资比特币的美国交易所交易基金每日净流入量创下 13.8 亿美元的纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/us-bitcoin-btc-etfs-including-blackrock-s-ibit-get-record-inflows</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 06:48:10 GMT</pubDate>
